data.description: SILVERADO RANCH BEAUTY!  4 bedrooms with a pool!  Huge great room with wet bar just off of the kitchen! Granite counter tops with dark kitchen cabinets! Downstairs is all custom tile flooring! Custom primary bath, counter tops and shower are spectacular! Primary bedroom has wood floors and a balcony over looking the sparkling pool! Downstairs bath has custom counters and sink as well!  Crown molding, ceiling fans and window coverings throughout!  Close proximity to schools, shopping, restaurants, freeway and more!
